---
title: Bangin' Chorizo and Egg Breakfast Burger with Spicy Mayo Sauce and Potato Dippers
description: Breakfast for dinner is the name of the game, and this recipe is playing for keeps! Spiced chorizo sausage patties, golden runny yolk eggs, spicy mayo and crunchy tart pickles are stacked on toasted brioche buns to bring sunshine to your table. A side of paprika spiced potato wedges and chive dipping sauce make this a recipe for dinner time success!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/burgers-dejeuner-au-chorizo-et-aux-oeufs-502f692c.jpg
